        ___       &kp Q           &kp W          &kp E           &kp R              &kp T  &to WINDOWS                                                           &none        &kp Y  &kp U           &kp I              &kp O            &kp P     &kp BSLH
        &kp LSHFT &hm_l SYS A     &kp S          &hm_l EXTEND D  &hm_l APP F        &kp G  &kp DEL         &kp LCTRL &kp LALT &kp LGUI  &kp RCTRL                &kp BSPC     &kp H  &kp J           &kp K              &kp L            &hm_r SYS SEMI  &kp SQT
